{"tid":1239950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次林鄭記者會小量資料整理（含主觀）","createTime":"2019-06-18T08:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:50:17.000Z","uid":41292,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2828e5f48baf2c0edb3fc54378799622841f0e2a","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"只係聽左少少 有幾個人聽唔切 仲有我英文比較差記唔切<br />\n所以只係記左中文<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">問題</span><br />\n<br />\n1.五大so求<br />\n2.道歉對象 點解人地先？<br />\n3.會唔會再整23條依啲閪條例<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n<br />\n1.機制<br />\n6月15號停左無再推動，因引起矛盾和紛爭，未解決就唔重啟<br />\n2.佢話最重要係今次致歉，佢話佢係負最大責任對大家致歉<br />\n3未來管制會困難，係因為對政府嘅信心，佢地會加倍努力去管治香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">問題</span><br />\n1.五個so求係答應，點解你會覺得人地會接受<br />\n2.點解係stop唔係cancel，係咪為左面子<br />\n3.暴動嘅定性，係咪同一哥嘅說法一樣？<br />\n4.道歉係咪道歉埋支持修例個啲人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n1+4:因為政府係依個修例做得不足，所以先會咁，所以係向全港市民道歉，係all of about，係佢嘅責任<br />\n2.講過唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.叫一哥問律政司，但係又話佢講得好清楚，係唔需要怕有暴動責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">TVB</span><br />\n<br />\n1.點解唔講cancel<br />\n2.問責制係咪無用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n<br />\n1.講過好多次<br />\n2.有好多野政府需要處理，比機會佢地做野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">有線</span><br />\n<br />\n1.會唔會重啟<br />\n2.收返暴動？<br />\n3.警察濫用暴力嘅問題<br />\n4.你覺得自己係修例犯左啲咩錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n1.解決曬所有紛爭同矛盾先會考慮重啟，如果今次立法會任期前都搞唔到就會失效！<br />\n2.按警務處要求先講，香港人唔會接受暴動，政府嘅立場係按一哥嘅說法。<br />\n3.香港係有投訴機制，有監警會 屌你老母！有撚用<br />\n4.佢話自己工作不足，係多方面嘅不足。如想有法治，強化同外國嘅刑事合作，好難做到客觀嘅工作，佢地係解說方面做得唔夠！ 我屌你老母臭閪 收皮喇屌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">問題</span><br />\n<br />\n1.今次死左人，會唔會為左佢而負責，而落台<br />\n2.有啲警察無no點投<br />\n3.有啲人連跑都比人告暴動<br />\n4.會唔會秋後算帳？<br />\n5.一直唔講撤回，2020年7月前會唔會再2讀<br />\n6.點解讀記你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n1.用和平理性嘅方法去表達，佢對死人好難過，佢想做好多野，所以唔撚落台<br />\n2.有機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />投訴 屌你老母點撚樣投呀<br />\n3.按一哥嘅說話<br />\n5.無修例時間表，要解決紛爭矛盾先會繼續，如果2020年7月都搞唔到就接受<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"> 港台</span><br />\n<br />\n1.有好多人唔想你做呀<br />\n2.你同建制派嘅關係<br />\n3.陳同佳點處理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n3.做唔到 因為無修例所以做唔到 令佢覺得遺憾<br />\n1.佢有熱誠繼續做，好依兩年做嘅野好受人歡迎，啲人提點佢唔好停落力，比左動力佢繼續做。<br />\n3.有爭議同有分歧，有人寫左文章同埋行動，對佢地有歉意，以後嘅事要對事不對人，想同各派議員合作，同建制派嘅合作機會多，希望會做到野"},{"pid":"44912c691b6aa7b8c61e9d8fd41c15c7229f43de","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:59:28.000Z","msg":"尾二佢真係答左咁多<br />\n<br />\n我盡量記錄曬佢講嘅野"},{"pid":"f4705d74fa3d82b1ec78318f3326f154f57282ea","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"e6bb36c3838a73db3cdb9cdb4021d830ff118386","tid":1239950,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5b4c3ca0d6fae840ffd5ced4374f8cabf4fe8f","tid":1239950,"uid":228715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"做咩唔答人記你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116893ae440536970b739bd89ec89dd376d30482","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"我遲左聽 所以前面靠巴打補充<br />\n中間都有個記者miss左 因為爆左5001搵緊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e182255533bfaf58b2c52666473e48d1b20bdef5","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce5b4c3ca0d6fae840ffd5ced4374f8cabf4fe8f","tid":1239950,"uid":228715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"做咩唔答人記你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"點撚知佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd293f36eb1dd10776df7438b3dc76a89410632","tid":1239950,"uid":626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"唔該晒巴打"},{"pid":"0f487dd9a137ecf2ac65be4397ce5d925d23bf6e","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"港台有監警會直播"},{"pid":"8b06990da61ef7f764fbb6c3154aab1fef7871ec","tid":1239950,"uid":108443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"點解我睇完都唔知佢up咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4631733ef603c3c3e98a8eef8c59c40b0262029d","tid":1239950,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 失效？咁23條又點解釋啊閪婆"},{"pid":"8ef0ad63451d15c6214416f309696ec22525a751","tid":1239950,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e182255533bfaf58b2c52666473e48d1b20bdef5","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce5b4c3ca0d6fae840ffd5ced4374f8cabf4fe8f","tid":1239950,"uid":228715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"做咩唔答人記你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"點撚知佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"有答呀，話唔滿意去投訴警察啦"},{"pid":"22100b3528fde6f377d968e0ce0ed8a65ef98f0e","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"監警會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Apple</span><br />\n<br />\n1.速龍無號碼，而佢地用好大武力，但係我地無方法去識別佢地，就算議員在場都拒絕透露，警方係有系統性隱藏自己嘅身份，監警會有咩立場同埋要求警方改進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">答</span><br />\n1.主席：要睇投訴人點講，無證據係手上，聽到你地嘅投訴係會幫你討論下講。 <br />\n秘書長：覺得自己唔公平對待係要投訴，佢地會跟進無身份認證嘅問題，會整合一個報告，交比警察改善。"},{"pid":"d9f292ec35412142ad2f919b78e6d447889cfe59","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:23:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">明報</span><br />\n<br />\n1.監警會點睇民間想整個獨立委員會調查事件。<br />\n2.警察嘅武力好多人關注，你地會點做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">答</span><br />\n1.主席：政府想做唔會反對，盡佢地所能<br />\n2.主席：有人投訴就會做，佢地都會關注大場面同埋政策"},{"pid":"5052a469043ca57f424480ae97692b5038e5cc79","tid":1239950,"uid":195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fHvA2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fHvA2S.png&h=3a0235d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdee4b4ad609837d8c3e871de6127be5ab0de004","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:31:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港電台</span><br />\n<br />\n1.6月9開始 監警會無去到現在，有啲咩原因去唔到<br />\n<br />\n2.專責小組同獨立委員會嘅限制係邊？你會點選？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n1.主席：無派人因為無警察照顧到佢地<br />\n2.主席：例如處理地鐵同埋巴士嘅獨立委員會係司法問題，佢地無得搞。佢地同黑警無關係，所以佢地會專注去了解。<br />\n秘書長：專責小組佢地同各方人有緊密聯繫，佢地有一直做野，如記者協會嘅投訴，佢地有即時同警方聯繫。佢地考慮日後做咩都會公佈。小組人員希望係專業，同埋同一個標準，個team會處理由6月9號開始嘅事件"},{"pid":"3a131d279090bd1ddbdd188c7bc67ad6a076fa3d","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">都市日報</span><br />\n<br />\n1.有冇初步報告出黎？幾時？<br />\n2.有好多次示威，你地有無啲乜野建議係做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n<br />\n2.有比過傳媒溝通嘅建議，佢地會同示威人士係現場溝通。<br />\n佢地收到好多記協嘅投訴係會跟進，今次係比佔中同旺角事件多好多投訴。<br />\n<br />\n1.會處理個別個案先，會抽啲制度問題先，再做特別報告，比唔到時間出黎。佢地會有幾個月一次有公開會議，個陣可以問下進度"},{"pid":"d9b6d06b0d964ca2bfc895578b3a17f42ede9266","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"屌唔撚想聽監警會個個"},{"pid":"de4f3cd3b4844b0143f4797d25097e1e0de426c0","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港01</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.6月9號，16號點解唔出去？<br />\n2.點回應水平線嘅發射子彈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回答</span><br />\n1.佢地出左去就變左證人，需要申報利益，所以佢地要好有系統咁決定出唔出去，要大量時間先落去睇。佢地要睇曬全面，落到去就只係睇到少少，所以唔去。今次好多資料，佢地一直有睇資料。6月9號11點開始睇。佢地需要客觀嘅證據。<br />\n2.唔可以咁早評論，要去睇全面，前後左右嘅情況"},{"pid":"d661738f0a2a4939e3160153dd5587a14f60ba01","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"問題<br />\n1.有關於中信嘅問題<br />\n2.會唔會搵網上嘅資料同埋片段？<br />\n<br />\n回答<br />\n<br />\n1.佢地依定做唔到判斷，但係覺得好唔理想<br />\n2.佢地會一直係網上搵片，會搵有關嘅片。"},{"pid":"b70a50eb57e929f1fc70438147028637f1a41c96","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"問題<br />\n1.專責小組嘅角色？<br />\n<br />\n回答<br />\n<br />\n1.處理投訴係有兩層機制<br />\n一、要接受投訴<br />\n二、監警"},{"pid":"49256e541bbd09e952cc6dedb95167979c7056de","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b70a50eb57e929f1fc70438147028637f1a41c96","tid":1239950,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"問題<br />\n1.專責小組嘅角色？<br />\n<br />\n回答<br />\n<br />\n1.處理投訴係有兩層機制<br />\n一、要接受投訴<br />\n二、監警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"聽到唔想聽 對唔住各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}